ent-ClothingMaskGasCPCivilProtectionMask = civil defense unit helmet
    .desc = A standard blue tactical helmet with an armored visor and a built-in audio channel for receiving orders. Its austere design transforms the face of a law enforcement officer into a faceless mask of Alliance law.
    .suffix = HL2
ent-ClothingMaskGasCPCivilProtectionMaskCommissar = helmet of the civil defense commissioner
    .desc = A distinctive white helmet with enhanced protection and an integrated communications system, symbolizing the highest administrative and punitive rank in the Civil Defense. Its color and impeccable appearance visually distinguish the wearer from ordinary units, emphasizing the right not only to enforce but also to administer the law.
    .suffix = HL2
ent-ClothingMaskGasCPCivilProtectionMaskDL = civil defense division leader's helmet
    .desc = An elite command helmet with silver accents, an integrated tactical display, and a cryptographic communications system. Its design emphasizes the status of the highest operational commander, whose orders coordinate entire suppression zones.
    .suffix = HL2
