ent-ClothingMaskGasCPModerngasMask = modern gas mask
    .desc = A tactical filtration system with a sealed mask, wide viewing window, and replaceable filters for protection against chemical, biological, and radiation threats. Its ergonomic design and low breathing resistance allow for effective operation even in highly contaminated environments.
