ent-ClothingMaskGasCPRussiaMask = soviet gas mask
    .desc = A reliable and simple Cold War-era defense system, constructed of durable rubber and metal with a distinctive round filter box. Its simple design and proven construction have saved thousands of lives in real and simulated chemical warfare situations.
    .suffix = HL2
ent-ClothingMaskGasCPSwatMask = SWAT gas mask
    .desc = A tactical protective mask with enhanced visibility, a communication system, and firearms compatibility. Designed for assault operations involving tear gas, smoke screens, or chemical threats.
    .suffix = HL2
